nodes.text: Heidi Shannon is a voice actress, making her debut with the Mask cartoon TV series, but afterwards concentrated on video game voicing. Her work includes several Star Wars titles. Most notable is the voicing of Mara Jade in Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Mysteries of the Sith and Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds.
